trans-unit.source: Represents a literal code fragment that can be compiled.
trans-unit.target: Representerar ett litteralt kodfragment som kan sammanställas.

trans-unit.source: CodeSnippetCompileUnit can represent a literal block of code that is included directly in the source without modification.
trans-unit.target: CodeSnippetCompileUnit kan representera en literal kodblock direkt i källan utan modifiering.

trans-unit.source: A CodeSnippetCompileUnit stores a section of code, exactly in its original format, as a string.
trans-unit.target: En CodeSnippetCompileUnit lagras en del av kod, exakt i dess ursprungliga format, som en sträng.

trans-unit.source: The CodeDOM does not translate literal code fragments.
Literal code fragments are stored and output in their original format.
trans-unit.target: Literalen kodfragment lagras och utdata i deras ursprungliga format.

trans-unit.source: CodeDOM objects that contain literal code are provided so developers can encapsulate code that is already in the target language.
trans-unit.target: CodeDOM-objekt som innehåller literal kod tillhandahålls så att utvecklare kan kapsla kod som redan finns på språket som mål.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeSnippetCompileUnit.Value%2A> property contains the literal code fragment as a string.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeSnippetCompileUnit.Value%2A>egenskapen innehåller literal kodfragmentet som en sträng.</xref:System.CodeDom.CodeSnippetCompileUnit.Value%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeSnippetCompileUnit.LinePragma%2A> property is optional and specifies the position of the code within a source code document.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeSnippetCompileUnit.LinePragma%2A>egenskapen är valfri och anger placeringen av koden i koden källdokument.</xref:System.CodeDom.CodeSnippetCompileUnit.LinePragma%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeSnippetCompileUnit"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeSnippetCompileUnit"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: If you use this constructor you should also set the <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeSnippetCompileUnit.Value%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Om du använder den här konstruktorn bör du också ange den <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeSnippetCompileUnit.Value%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.CodeDom.CodeSnippetCompileUnit.Value%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeSnippetCompileUnit"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeSnippetCompileUnit"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: The literal code fragment to represent.
Gets or sets the line and file information about where the code is located in a source code document.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger informationen rad och om var koden finns i ett källdokument kod.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeLinePragma"></xref> that indicates the position of the code fragment.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeLinePragma"> </xref> som anger positionen för kodfragmentet.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the literal code fragment to represent.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger literal kodfragmentet att representera.
